														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-399046">
									

<p>Regarding the Able example…</p>
<p>He's an unattainable super-powered badass. There will assuredly be <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">people</span> misguided fans who try to add incidents in which they (or their idealized Mary-Sue stand-ins) become the "victims" of "pranks" just like the one described.</p>
<p>Could you maybe add a rule about "no trying to write up your own fantasies with the excuse that they're actually the results of a 'prank'"?</p>

